      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>basa fillet</strong> over the <strong>sun-dried tomato sauce</strong> with the <strong>crispy</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong>, <strong>roasted garlic</strong> and <strong>green beans</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
